NOTE The limiting values of the ratio $f_u/f_y$, the elongation at failure and the ultimate strain $\varepsilon_u$ for steels greater than S460 up to S700 may be defined in the National Annex. The following values are recommended:

- $f_u/f_y \geq 1.05$;
- elongation at failure not less than 10%;
- $\varepsilon_u \geq 15f_y/E$.
